#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:2
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Installing the &kde-sc;"
msgid "Installing &plasma-desktop; and &kde; Applications"
msgstr "Installer &kde-sc;"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:4
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can install the &kde-sc; on a variety of different platforms, ranging "
#| "from smartphones and tablets to computers running &Microsoft; &Windows;, "
#| "&MacOS;, &UNIX;, &BSD; or &Linux;. Binary packages are available for many "
#| "different platforms and distributions, or advanced users may build the "
#| "source code."
msgid ""
"You can install &kde; applications, including &plasma-desktop;, on a variety "
"of different platforms, ranging from smartphones and tablets to computers "
"running &Microsoft; &Windows;, &macOS;, &UNIX;, &BSD; or &Linux;. Binary "
"packages are available for many different platforms and distributions, or "
"advanced users may build the source code."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez installer &kde-sc; sur toute une variété de plates-formes "
"différentes, allant des smart-phones et tablettes aux ordinateurs exécutant "
"&Microsoft; &Windows;, &MacOS;, &UNIX;, &BSD; ou &Linux;. Des paquets "
"binaires sont disponibles pour plusieurs plates-formes et distributions "
"différentes, ou les utilisateurs expérimentés peuvent aussi compiler le code "
"source."

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installing Packages"
msgstr "Installer des paquets"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:13
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Hundreds of developers worldwide have done a lot of work to make it easy "
#| "to install &kde; on a variety of different devices and platforms."
msgid ""
"Hundreds of developers worldwide have done a lot of work to make it easy to "
"install &kde; onto a variety of different devices and platforms."
msgstr ""
"Des centaines de développeurs internationaux ont accompli un énorme travail "
"pour rendre facile l'installation de &kde; sur une grande variété "
"d'appareils et de plates-formes différents."

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Linux;"
msgstr "&Linux;"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:19
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Nearly every &Linux; distribution provides binary packages for individual "
#| "&kde-sc; applications and the &plasma-workspaces; as a whole."
msgid ""
"Nearly every &Linux; distribution provides binary packages for individual "
"applications and the &plasma-desktop; as a whole."
msgstr ""
"Presque toutes les distributions &Linux; fournissent des paquets binaires "
"pour les applications individuelles de &kde-sc; et les &plasma-workspaces; "
"comme un tout."

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:22
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To install an individual application, look for its name in your "
#| "distribution's package collection. To install one of the &plasma-"
#| "workspaces;, like &plasma-desktop;, look for a metapackage or package "
#| "group, typically <literal>kde-desktop</literal>."
msgid ""
"To install an individual application, look for its name in your "
"distribution's package collection. To install one of the &plasma-"
"workspaces;, like &plasma-desktop;, look for a metapackage or package group, "
"typically <literal>plasma-desktop</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Pour installer une application individuellement, recherchez son nom dans la "
"bibliothèque de paquets de votre distribution. Pour en installer une de "
"l'&plasma-workspaces;, comme le &plasma-desktop;, recherchez un meta-paquet "
"ou un paquet-groupe, <literal>kde-desktop</literal> typiquement."

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:28
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Some core applications may be installed together with other core "
#| "applications in a combined package named after the &kde; package they are "
#| "provided in. For instance, &dolphin; might be found in the <literal>kde-"
#| "baseapps</literal> package."
msgid ""
"Some applications may be installed together with other applications in a "
"combined package named after the &kde; package they are provided in. For "
"instance, &konqueror; might be found in the <literal>kde-baseapps</literal> "
"package."
msgstr ""
"Quelques applications de base peuvent être installées avec d'autres "
"applications de base dans un paquet combiné qui porte le nom d'un paquet "
"&kde; dans lequel elles sont fournies. Par exemple, &dolphin; peut être "
"trouvé dans le paquet <literal>kde-baseapps</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:34
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you have trouble locating &kde; packages for your distribution, please "
#| "contact their support resources. Many distributions also have a team "
#| "dedicated to packaging &kde; that can provide assistance specific to &kde;"
msgid ""
"If you have trouble locating &kde; packages for your distribution, please "
"contact their support resources. Many distributions also have a team "
"dedicated to packaging applications by &kde; that can provide assistance "
"specific to them."
msgstr ""
"Si vous avez des problèmes pour trouver des paquets &kde; pour votre "
"distribution, contactez leurs ressources d'aide. Plusieurs distributions ont "
"aussi une équipe dédiée à la création de paquets pour &kde; qui peut vous "
"fournir de l'aide spécifique à &kde;"

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Microsoft; &Windows;"
msgstr "&Microsoft; &Windows;"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:45
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The &kde; on Windows Initiative provides binary packages of &kde-sc; "
#| "applications for &Microsoft; &Windows;. They also provide a special "
#| "installer application that permits you to install individual applications "
#| "or groups and all necessary dependencies easily."
msgid ""
"The &kde; on Windows Initiative provides binary packages of &kde; "
"applications for &Microsoft; &Windows;. They also provide a special "
"installer application that permits you to install individual applications or "
"groups and all necessary dependencies easily."
msgstr ""
"Le projet &kde; sur Windows fournit des paquets binaires des applications de "
"&kde-sc; pour &Microsoft; &Windows;. Il fournit aussi un installateur "
"d'applications spécial qui vous permet d'installer facilement des "
"applications individuellement ou en groupe et toutes les dépendances "
"nécessaires."

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:50
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For more information on the initiative and to download the installer, "
#| "visit <ulink url=\"http://windows.kde.org/\">the KDE on Windows "
#| "Initiative</ulink>."
msgid ""
"For more information on the initiative and to download the installer, visit "
"<ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/Windows\">the KDE on Windows "
"Initiative</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Pour plus d'informations sur ce projet et télécharger l'installateur, "
"visitez <ulink url=\"http://windows.kde.org/\">le projet KDE sur Windows</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:59
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "&MacOS;"
msgid "&macOS;"
msgstr "&MacOS;"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:61
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Individual &kde-sc; applications can be installed through several "
#| "different <quote>ports</quote> systems available for &MacOS;. Several "
#| "different &kde; applications also provide their own binary builds for "
#| "&MacOS;."
msgid ""
"Individual &kde; applications can be installed through several different "
"<quote>ports</quote> systems available for &macOS;. Several different &kde; "
"applications also provide their own binary builds for &macOS;."
msgstr ""
"Les applications individuelles de &kde-sc; peuvent être installées à travers "
"plusieurs <quote>ports</quote> systèmes différents disponibles pour &MacOS;. "
"Plusieurs applications &kde; différentes fournissent aussi leurs propres "
"binaires compilés pour &MacOS;."

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:65
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For more information, visit <ulink url=\"http://mac.kde.org/\">&kde; on "
#| "&MacOS;X</ulink>."
msgid ""
"For more information, visit <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/Mac"
"\">&kde; on &macOS;</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Pour plus d'informations, visitez <ulink url=\"http://mac.kde.org/\"> &kde; "
"sur &MacOS;X</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "&BSD;"
msgstr "&BSD;"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:73
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Most &BSD; distributions allows you to install &kde-sc; applications and "
#| "the &plasma-workspaces; as a whole through their <quote>ports</quote> "
#| "system."
msgid ""
"Most &BSD; distributions allows you to install &kde; applications and the "
"&plasma-desktop; through their <quote>ports</quote> system."
msgstr ""
"La plupart des distributions &BSD; vous permettent d'installer des "
"applications de &kde-sc; et des &plasma-workspaces; comme un tout grâce à "
"leurs <quote>ports</quote> systèmes."

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information on installing ports, see your &BSD; distribution's "
"documentation."
msgstr ""
"Pour plus d'informations sur l'installation des ports, allez voir la "
"documentation &BSD; de votre distribution."

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mobile Devices"
msgstr "Appareils mobiles"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:86
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&plasma-active; is an exciting initiative to bring a new &kde; experience "
#| "to mobile devices like smartphones or tablets. Binary releases are "
#| "provided for several different devices."
msgid ""
"<productname>Plasma Mobile</productname> is an exciting initiative to bring "
"a new &kde; experience to mobile devices like smartphones or tablets. Binary "
"releases are provided for several different devices."
msgstr ""
"&plasma-active; est un projet excitant qui apporte une nouvelle expérience "
"&kde; aux appareils mobiles tels que les smart-phones ou tablettes. Des "
"binaires sont fournis pour plusieurs appareils différents."

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:90
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For more information, visit <ulink url=\"http://plasma-active.org/"
#| "\">&plasma-active;</ulink>."
msgid ""
"For more information, visit <ulink url=\"https://www.plasma-mobile.org/"
"\"><productname>Plasma Mobile</productname></ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Pour plus d'informations, visitez <ulink url=\"http://plasma-active.org/"
"\">&plasma-active;</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "Live Media"
msgstr "Média de démarrage"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:98
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Several &Linux; and &BSD; distributions offer live media. This permits "
#| "you to try out the &plasma-workspaces; without installing anything to "
#| "your system. All you have to do insert a CD or connect a USB drive and "
#| "boot from it. If you like what you see, most offer an option to install "
#| "it to your hard drive."
msgid ""
"Several &Linux; and &BSD; distributions offer live media. This permits you "
"to try out the &plasma-desktop; without installing anything to your system. "
"All you have to do insert a CD or connect a USB drive and boot from it. If "
"you like what you see, most offer an option to install it to your hard drive."
msgstr ""
"Plusieurs distributions &Linux; et &BSD; offrent un média de démarrage. Cela "
"vous permet d'essayer l'&plasma-workspaces; sans installer quoi que ce soit "
"sur votre système. Tout ce que vous avez à faire est d'insérer un CD ou de "
"connecter un média USB et de démarrer à partir de ce dernier. Si vous "
"appréciez ce que vous voyez, la plupart des média de démarrage proposent une "
"option pour l'installer sur votre disque dur."

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:103
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "There is <ulink url=\"http://www.kde.org/download/distributions.php\">a "
#| "list of distributions that offer the &kde-sc; on live media</ulink> on "
#| "the &kde; website."
msgid ""
"There is <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/download/distributions.php\">a "
"list of distributions that offer the &kde; workspace and applications on "
"live media</ulink> on the &kde; website."
msgstr ""
"Il existe <ulink url=\"http://www.kde.org/download/distributions.php\"> une "
"liste de distributions qui proposent &kde-sc; sur un média de démarrage</"
"ulink> sur le site web de &kde;."

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "Building from Source Code"
msgstr "Compiler à partir du code source"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:110
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For detailed information on how to compile and install &kde; applications "
#| "see <ulink url=\"http://techbase.kde.org/"
#| "Getting_Started#Building_and_Running_KDE_Software_From_Source\"> Building "
#| "and Running &kde; Software From Source on &kde; TechBase</ulink>."
msgid ""
"For detailed information on how to compile and install &plasma-desktop; and "
"applications see <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/"
"Guidelines_and_HOWTOs/Build_from_source\">Build from source</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Pour des informations détaillées sur la manière de compiler et d'installer "
"des applications &kde; allez voir <ulink url=\"http://techbase.kde.org/"
"Getting_Started#Building_and_Running_KDE_Software_From_Source\"> Compiler et "
"exécuter les applications &kde; à partir des sources dans la base technique "
"de &kde;</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since &kde; software uses <command>cmake</command> you should have no "
"trouble compiling it. Should you run into problems please report them to the "
"&kde; mailing lists."
msgstr ""
"Puisque &kde; utilise <command>cmake</command> vous ne devriez pas avoir de "
"problèmes à la compilation. Si vous rencontrez des problèmes, reportez-les à "
"la liste de diffusion de &kde;. "

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:117
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For detailed information on how to compile and install &kde; applications "
#| "see <ulink url=\"http://techbase.kde.org/"
